headline: More Americans Know Their Streaming Platform Passwords by Heart Than Their Cholesterol Score, New Survey Reveals
summary: questhealth.com, the consumer-initiated testing platform from Quest Diagnostics (NYSE: DGX), one of the nation's leading providers of diagnostic information services, today revealed the results of its second "Know Your Health" survey, conducted online by The Harris Poll among nearly 2,100 U.S. adults.
